cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SI

The paper discusses a measure of divergence and cross entropy, which are commonly used in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The authors propose a new measure and compare it to other bounded measures, which involves data analysis and statistical inference (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the properties of the measures and their applications, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SI).
